हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: A struggling young man stumbles upon mysterious superpowers, thrusting him into a world of corporate betrayal, dangerous enemies, and unexpected allies. As he learns to harness his new abilities, he must fight not just for survival, but for the people he cares about and the truth behind his powers. Watch Now!
